  <note>
    <title>Cholelithiasis with acute and chronic cholecystitis, gallbladder, laparoscopic  cholecystectomy</title>
    <created>20160909T071041Z</created>
    <updated>20231017T033421Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>The gallbladder shows focal ulcerative mucosa with purulent exudates superimposed on chronic cholecystitis. The wall shows hyperemia with extravasation of RBCs. No evidence of malignancy is noted.</div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
