    <updated>20250219T032558Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
      <source>desktop.win</source>
      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>chronic colitis.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows colonic mucosal tissue with lymphoplasmacytic infiltrate within the lamina propria, and preserved crypt architecture.</div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">No viral inclusion is highlighted by anti-CMV immunostain. No malignancy is observed.</span></div><div><br/></div><div>Ancillary studies: </div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Immunohistochemical stain:     CMV.</span></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
