    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Cytomegalovirus infection</span></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Microscopic description:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px;">Some scattered stromal or endothelial cells with eosinophilic nuclear inclusion are identified. Immunohistochemically, the viral</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px;">inclusion are highlighted by anti-CMV immunostain.</span></div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>COL8 Cauterized Hyperplastic Polyp [COL8]</title>
