      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Cauterized hyperplastic polyp.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows cautery artifact in hyperplastic polyp resulting in elongated, and stratified nuclei. Luminal serrations and prominent collagen band are seen.</div><div>        </div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
