<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>consistent with hypertrophied papillae.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows polypoid tissue revealing thin squamous epithelium overlying an edematous stroma with small, thin, branching vessels.</div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
