<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><br/></div><div>External hemorrhoid.</div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Microscopic description:</span></div><div>The slide reveals anal mucosal tissue which exhibits markedly congested or dilated vessels that are filled with RBCs.        </div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>Features suggestive of Brunner&apos;s gland hyperplasia; duodenum</title>
