    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Features suggestive of Brunner's gland hyperplasia.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Sections show benign duodenal mucosal tissues comprising prominent Brunner's gland</div><div>lobules with focal cystic dilatations lying deep to muscularis mucosa, probably</div><div>Brunner's gland hyperplasia. No malignancy is observed.</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
