      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Fistula with abscess formation.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>The section reveals a squamous-lined tissue in which a granulation-line fistulous tract is noted, extending from the squamous surface into the inner and deeper connective tissue stroma. There is accompanying round cell as well as polymorphonuclear cell infiltration around the tract and its adjacent tissue. Focal abscess formation is seen.    </div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
