  <note>
    <title>SCC, MD</title>
    <created>20161128T072518Z</created>
    <updated>20251121T092229Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Squamous cell carcinoma, moderately differentiated</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows sheets of neoplastic squamous cells revealing distinct nuclear pleomorphism and mitotic activity with stromal invasion.  Intercellular bridges and dyskeratosis are seen.</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>(This case has been reviewed by two pathologists.)</div><hr/><div><br/></div><div>Squamous cell carcinoma, moderately differentiated.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows nests of neoplastic squamous cells revealing distinct nuclear pleomorphism and mitotic activity with stromal invasion. </div><div>By immunohistochemistry, the tumor cells are positive for p40, confirming the diagnosis.</div><div><br/></div><div>        </div><div>(This case has been reviewed by two pathologists.)</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>未命名記事</title>
    <created>20200529T033201Z</created>
    <updated>20200529T033430Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
      <source>desktop.win</source>
      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Sessile serrated lesion with dysplasia. </div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows a sessile serrated lesion with dilated and L-shaped crypt bases. There is focal low-grade dysplasia revealing irregular serrated pattern with hyperchromatic and stratified nuclei.</div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>未命名記事</title>
    <created>20180501T085205Z</created>
    <updated>20180501T085209Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
