    <updated>20250424T044051Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
      <source>desktop.win</source>
      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Cauterized tubular adenoma.</div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Microscopic description:</span></div><div>Section shows severe cautery artifact making the cytologic interpretation difficult. There are crowded tubuloglandular structures consistent with tubular adenoma.</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>TA at least</title>
    <created>20180530T032252Z</created>
    <updated>20241125T023836Z</updated>
