      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Ulceration with Helicobacter pylori infection</span></div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>The gastric tissue fragments reveal partial destruction of the mucosa with marked infiltration by mixed inflammatory cells in the lamina propria. Necrotic debris are seen over the destructed surface as well as separate fragments. </div><div><br/></div><div>Helicobacter pylori microorganisms are identified in the surface of the adjacent mucosa and in the gastric pits. </div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="color:rgb(34, 34, 34);">No invasive carcinoma is demonstrated by AE1/AE3.</span></span></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-size: 9pt;"><span style="color:rgb(34, 34, 34);">Ancillary studies:</span></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 9pt;"><span style="color:rgb(34, 34, 34);">1. Special stain: Giemsa stain.</span></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 9pt;"><span style="color:rgb(34, 34, 34);">2. Immunohistochemical stain: AE1/AE3.</span></span></div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>Ulcer 沒bi到 [noulcer]</title>
