<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Vascular ectasia</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Some dilated mucosal capillaries are seen in the lamina</div><div>propria. The colonic glands are unremarkable.</div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
