<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Villous adenoma</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>It shows a polypoid tissue composed of fingerlike projections in which individual villus is lined by tall columnar epithelium featuring hyperchromatism and pseudostratification of the nuclei. No stromal invasion as to suggest malignant transformation is noted.</div></en-note>      ]]>
